## Hugo-integration

Hugo bruger sit eget content-system, men du kan skrive et lille script der konverterer @webhouse/cms JSON til Hugo's front matter + markdown format ved build-tid.

## Caching

Brug en `sync.Map` eller in-memory cache med TTL:

```go
var cache sync.Map

func (c *Client) CollectionCached(name, locale string) ([]Document, error) {
    key := name + ":" + locale
    if v, ok := cache.Load(key); ok {
        return v.([]Document), nil
    }
    docs, err := c.Collection(name, locale)
    if err != nil {
        return nil, err
    }
    cache.Store(key, docs)
    return docs, nil
}
```

